quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Tewali kingaana kulayira lunaku lwakuzuukira
  75,2,Era nga bwewatali kingaana kulayira omwoyo ogwejjusa
  75,3,Abaffe omuntu alowooza nti tetugenda kusobola kuzzaawo magumbage
  75,4,Nedda tukisobolera ddala nga bwetulisobola okuzzaawo ennwe zaabwe
  75,5,Wabula omuntu emirundi egisinga ayagala nnyo okuwangaalira mu kwonoona
  75,6,Ngabuuza (mu ngeri ey'okujerega n'okuwakanya) nti olunaku lwokuzuukira lulibaawo ddi
  75,7,Ddala lugenga kubaawo nga n'amaaso g'abantu galiralambala olwokutya
  75,8,Ekitangala kyomwezi kigenda kuggwawo
  75,9,Enjuba n'omwezi birigattibwa (nga tewakyasobola kubaawo kiro namisana)
  75,10,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kwebuuza nti nzirukirewa
  75,11,"Kyekyo ddala, tewagenda kubaawo muntu weyekweka"
  75,12,Obuddo ku lunaku olwo bujja kuba eri Mukama Katondawo
  75,13,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kutegeezebwa ebyo byonna byeyakola nebyataakola
  75,14,Wabula ate ddala omuntu ye yennyini amanyi bye yakola ne byataakola (newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayeetonda)
  75,15,Newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayetonda
  75,16,Bwoba osoma Kur'ani toyanguyiriza nga olowooza nti kyekinakuyamba okuginyweeza
  75,17,Anti okugikungaanya kuli kuffe nga era bwekiri kuffe okunywereza ku lulimi lwo ensoma ennungi
  75,18,Kale nno bwetumala okugikusomera (nga tugiyisa ku Jiburilu) goberera ensoma yaayo
  75,19,Era mazima okuginnyonnyola kuli kuffe
  75,20,(Ebyo ebyogeddwa waggulu bimala omuntu okwebuulirira nabyo) wabula ebyembi mmwe mwagala ebyokufuna byensi ebyamangu
  75,21,Nemuleka ebyolunaku lw’enkomerero
  75,22,Ebyenyi bya bantu abamu ku lunaku olwo bigenda kuba nga bitemagana
  75,23,Bigenda kutunula ku Mukama Katonda waabyo
  75,24,Ate nga ebyenyi bya bantu abalala bigenda kuba binyikaavu
  75,25,Nga bimanyidde ddala nti bigenda kutuukibwako akabi akanene akamenya nenkizi
  75,26,Naye omwoyo bwegutuuka mu ddokooli
  75,27,Abantu webagambira nti ani alina eddagala eriyinza okumuwonya
  75,28,Wabula yye ngamaze okukakasa nti agenda kufa
  75,29,Entumbwe ne yeegatta ku ntumbwe
  75,30,Olwo nno obuddo buba busigadde eri Katondawo
  75,31,Naye nga omufu teyasaddaaka wadde okusaala
  75,32,Wabula yalimbisa ebigambo bya Katonda nabyesamba
  75,33,Olwo nno naatambula nadda eri abantu be nga yeeraga
  75,34,(Aligambibwa nti ekyo) ekikutuuseeko kikugwanidde era ddala kikugwanidde (owange ggwe omwonoonyi)
  75,35,Ate era kikugwanidde ng'ate era ddala kikugwanidde
  75,36,Omuntu alowooza nti ayinza okulekwa neyeeyisa nga bwayagala
  75,37,Tajjukira nti yasooka kuba tondo lyamazzi agazaala agateekebwa mu nabaana
  75,38,"Oluvanyuma naafuuka ekisayisayi, olwo Katonda naamutonda namussaako byonna ebimufuula omuntu"
  75,39,"Nga bwatyo bwakola emitendera ebiri, omusajja n'omukazi"
  75,40,Abaffe oyo eyakola omuntu mu ngeri eyo tasobola kulamusa bafu